+#!/usr/bin/env python3
+import requests
@@ -1,0 +4,45 @@
+base_url = "http://the-agent-company.com:8929"
+auth = ("root", "theagentcompany")
+
+
+def get_projects():
+    projects = []
+    page = 1
+    per_page = 100
+    while True:
+        response = requests.get(f"{base_url}/api/v4/projects", auth=auth, params={"page": page, "per_page": per_page})
+        if response.status_code != 200:
+            print("Error retrieving projects.", response.status_code, response.text)
+            break
+        current = response.json()
+        if not current:
+            break
+        projects.extend(current)
+        if len(current) < per_page:
+            break
+        page += 1
+    return projects
+
+
+def delete_project(project_id):
+    response = requests.delete(f"{base_url}/api/v4/projects/{project_id}", auth=auth)
+    if response.status_code in [200, 202]:
+        print(f"Project {project_id} deleted successfully.")
+    else:
+        print(f"Error deleting project {project_id}. Status: {response.status_code} Response: {response.text}")
+
+
+def main():
+    projects = get_projects()
+    for project in projects:
+        fullname = project.get("path_with_namespace")
+        if fullname != "root/sotopia":
+            print(f"Deleting project: {fullname} (ID: {project.get('id')})")
+            delete_project(project.get("id"))
+        else:
+            print(f"Skipping project: {fullname}")
+
+
+if __name__ == "__main__":
+    main()
+
